  "updated": 1781441295,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a2870888b76b858a358d681",
      "text": "ボディバッグおじさん",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1781035146,
      "updated": 1781035146
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2ea2c80000000000da2352",
      "text": "感情強めなので画像蓋しておこう[https://gyazo.com/82cb872fa9fa23d09bdeecda4b2ddebd]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781441224,
      "updated": 1781441295
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2ea2ce0000000000da2353",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781441230,
      "updated": 1781441230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2870870000000000371d00",
      "text": "[「ボディバッグおじさん」が盛り上がっているが、結局男が身に着けて似合うバッグを発明できなかったファッション業界全体の敗北だと思う→本当におじさんに合うバッグはないのか？で議論 - Togetter https://togetter.com/li/2707489]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1781035146,
      "updated": 1781035148
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2870870000000000371d01",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/c2f1913196e3d75589d631c5c970e959]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1781035146,
      "updated": 1781035149
    },
    {
      "id": "6a28708b0000000000371d08",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1781035150,
      "updated": 1781035150
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2870870000000000371d02",
      "text": "真面目な話、貴重品身に付けながらも動きやすい、をしたいなら唯一の手段だと思う[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1781035146,
      "updated": 1781035154
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2870870000000000371d03",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/fccbd70d7f678896244b616252781915]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1781035146,
      "updated": 1781035155
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2870870000000000371d04",
      "text": "\t\t財布とか入れた状態でもシャッフルダンスできる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1781035146,
      "updated": 1781035160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2870870000000000371d05",
      "text": "\tただこれはボディバッグというより[ウエストポーチ]？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781035146,
      "updated": 1781066756
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2870870000000000371d06",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1781035146,
      "updated": 1781035165
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2926d20000000000af6217",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1781081811,
      "updated": 1781081811
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2926d20000000000af6218",
      "text": "利便性とおしゃれって両立しなそう[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1781081811,
      "updated": 1781081825
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2ea2610000000000da234c",
      "text": " [利便性とおしゃれの両立]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781441121,
      "updated": 1781441127
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2ea2680000000000da234d",
      "text": " [おしゃれだけど使いづらいもの]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781441128,
      "updated": 1781441131
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2926d50000000000af6219",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1781081813,
      "updated": 1781081813
    },
    {
      "id": "6a294662000000000031c7e5",
      "text": "これがかっこよくない理由の考察があって面白い[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1781089890,
      "updated": 1781089917
    },
    {
